OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Fheavy rain and strong winds will move
OL,7,Feastwards this evening. Rain clearing
OL,8,Fduring the early hours allowing some
OL,9,Fclearer spells and a few showers to
OL,10,Ffollow.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA brighter day on Wednesday
OL,13,Fwith a mix of cloud and sunny spells.
OL,14,FA few showers possible, especially
OL,15,Fnear north and west facing coasts.
OL,16,FWinds easing with temperatures near
OL,17,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
