OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FWet
OL,6,Fand windy on Thursday with gales
OL,7,Fpossible for a time. Colder on Friday
OL,8,Fwith blustery showers, occasionally
OL,9,Fwintry over the hills. Drier and less
OL,10,Fcold on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
